full_description: code.talks is Northern Germany's largest developer conference – since 2010. On November 4–5, 2026, around 3,500 developers, tech leads, and CTOs come together at Kinopolis Hamburg. 100+ speakers, 14 tracks, two days of talks, deep dives, and community. 2026 motto: The code has changed.

